title: Ableton Live 8 v8.0.1
description:
100% Clean no virus

This is Ableton Live 8 V8.0.1 Working !

**Important**
After installing the software, DO NOT start the program, copy Live 8.0.1.exe provided into the subfolder ~/Ableton/live 8.0.1/program/

No serial number to enter.

If library is empty install live packs from directory ~/Ableton/Live 8.0.1/Resources/DefaultPackages/ and they will all work after.
